originalText.text: We knew we wanted to use Edward Winter as our photographer after our close friends used him for their engagement and wedding photos. When it came to our rainy day wedding this September at The Roundhouse we knew we were in the best hands. Eddie is calm, unobtrusive and a true artist. Somehow he caught the emotion of our day without it feeling like a production.

originalText.text: We feel so lucky to have had Eddie and Jules as our wedding photographers this past June at Tappan Hill Mansion. They brought such a calming, positive and easy going vibe to an expected hectic and stressful day. They were incredibly organized and timely, so much so, that we had extra time to take more portraits than we had allotted for. Looking through the hundreds and hundreds of photos we got back, Iâ€™m able to fully experience the day again through our guests eyes as Eddie and Jules were able to capture natural, candid photos of almost all of our guests at our 175 person wedding. They were able to capture such meaningful and beautiful shots without ever being intrusive - we hardly even noticed they were there throughout the night. Canâ€™t thank them enough!
